	<item>
		<title>Avnet Edge &#038; Beyond Tech Days 2026 (10 Jul 2026 &#8211; 24 Jul 2026)</title>
		<link>https://deepx.ai/avnet-edge-beyond-tech-days-2026-10-jul-2026-24-jul-2026/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[deepx_admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 08:39:10 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Event]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[avnet]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[APAC]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://deepx.ai/?p=13249</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Join Avnet Edge &#38; Beyond Tech Days 2026 at Singapore, Hanoi &#38; Ho Chi Minh, Vietnam.   Join Avnet Edge &#38; Beyond Tech Days 2026 — a regional technology conference and exhibition designed for engineers, product leaders, and decision‑makers navigating the next phase of AI, edge computing, and intelligent systems.   Taking place across Singapore, Hanoi, [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="13249" class="elementor elementor-13249" data-elementor-post-type="post">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b3e9acd e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="b3e9acd" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;jet_parallax_layout_list&quot;:[]}">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6578027 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="6578027" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
															<img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1024" height="192" src="https://cdn.deepx.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/10174134/2026-avnet-techday-1440x270-1-1024x192.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-13252" alt="" srcset="https://cdn.deepx.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/10174134/2026-avnet-techday-1440x270-1-1024x192.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.deepx.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/10174134/2026-avnet-techday-1440x270-1-300x56.jpg 300w, https://cdn.deepx.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/10174134/2026-avnet-techday-1440x270-1-768x144.jpg 768w, https://cdn.deepx.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/10174134/2026-avnet-techday-1440x270-1.jpg 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b850f09 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer" data-id="b850f09" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="spacer.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<div class="elementor-spacer">
			<div class="elementor-spacer-inner"></div>
		</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-35b4141 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="35b4141" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<h2 dir="ltr"><em>Join Avnet Edge &amp; Beyond Tech Days 2026 at Singapore, Hanoi &amp; Ho Chi Minh, Vietnam.</em></h2><div><em> </em></div><p dir="ltr">Join Avnet Edge &amp; Beyond Tech Days 2026 — a regional technology conference and exhibition designed for engineers, product leaders, and decision‑makers navigating the next phase of AI, edge computing, and intelligent systems.</p><p dir="ltr"> </p><p dir="ltr">Taking place across Singapore, Hanoi, and Ho Chi Minh City, this year’s Tech Days will bring together Avnet experts and a strong ecosystem of semiconductor and IP&amp;E partners to explore how innovation at the edge can be designed, scaled, and deployed in real‑world applications.</p><p dir="ltr"> </p><p dir="ltr">The event will showcase practical applications of AI and edge technologies across areas such as intelligent vision, industrial automation, voice and object detection, robotics, and scalable server‑to‑edge computing—with a focus on moving innovation from concept to deployment at scale.</p>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c696a02 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer" data-id="c696a02" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="spacer.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<div class="elementor-spacer">
			<div class="elementor-spacer-inner"></div>
		</div>
						</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2eccb8d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="2eccb8d" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;jet_parallax_layout_list&quot;:[]}">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3930159 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="3930159" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<h2 dir="ltr">Event details</h2><h5 dir="ltr"><strong>Date &amp; Location:  </strong>   </h5><ol><li dir="ltr">First stop: 10 July 2026 (Friday), 8:30am – 5:30pm / Sheraton, Singapore  </li><li dir="ltr">Second stop: 21 July 2026 (Tuesday), 8:30am – 5:00pm / JW Marriott, Hanoi</li><li dir="ltr">Third stop: 24 July 2026 (Friday), 8:30am – 5:00pm / Sheraton Saigon, Ho Chi Minh</li></ol><p dir="ltr"><strong>Registration Deadline: </strong><strong>Registration closes on 30 June 2026.</strong></p><p dir="ltr"> </p><h5 dir="ltr"><strong>Highlights of the event:</strong></h5><ul dir="ltr"><li>Keynote sessions featuring perspectives from Avnet Design Services, AI experts, and ecosystem partners</li><li>Live showcases of the latest AI and edge computing innovations through product exhibits and demonstrations </li><li>Networking opportunities and a lucky draw </li></ul>								</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4eaf21b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="4eaf21b" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;jet_parallax_layout_list&quot;:[]}">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5e61ec5 elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="5e61ec5" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<div class="elementor-button-wrapper">
					<a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://www.avnet.com/apac/resources/training-and-events/event/avnet-edge-beyond-techday-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
						<span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper">
									<span class="elementor-button-text">Register Now</span>
					</span>
					</a>
				</div>
								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a2139d2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer" data-id="a2139d2" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="spacer.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<div class="elementor-spacer">
			<div class="elementor-spacer-inner"></div>
		</div>
						</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				</div>
		]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
			</item>
